#	    test Kxxxx Axxx xx xx:
#	        1♦ (X) 1♠;
#	    test Kxxxx Axxx xx Ax:
#	        1♦ (X) 1♠;
	
#	1M => min-inv, 4 M, longest_or_equal M among >m & unbid;
